comments: Pritchard (BOS) cleanly deflects the ball away from Beverley (LAC).
Jackson (LAC) cleanly deflects the ball away from Brown (BOS).
Theis (BOS) makes contact with Beverley's (LAC) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Morris Sr. (LAC) is moving alongside Brown's (BOS) path and the two players make incidental contact on the perimeter.
Williams III (BOS) is already in Morris Sr.'s (LAC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Ibaka (LAC) maintains verticality as he defends Ojeleye's (BOS) shot near the rim.
Ibaka (LAC) makes contact with the ball as he defends Ojeleye's (BOS) shot attempt, and Ojeleye legally re-gains possession after his shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) and Jackson (LAC) make incidental foot to foot contact with one another off ball.
Replay review of the foul called on George (LAC) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful.  George avoids making contact to Tatum's (BOS) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Batum (LAC) legally contests Walker's (BOS) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Ibaka (LAC) is moving alongside Tatum's (BOS) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Tatum (BOS) loses control of the ball on his own prior to any contact from Jackson (LAC).
Walker (BOS) legally contests George's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Beverley (LAC) brushes Tatum's (BOS) arm during rebounding, and contact is marginal.
Williams III (BOS) is already in George's (LAC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Ibaka (LAC) is already in Tatum's (BOS) path when contact occurs and he releases away from the contact.
Tatum (BOS) legally contests George's (LAC) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Replay review of the foul called on Tatum (BOS) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Tatum extends his off-arm into George (LAC).
Jackson (LAC) commits a take foul on Williams III (BOS).
Ibaka (LAC) is already in Brown's (BOS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Ojeleye (BOS) legally contests George's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
George (LAC) commits a take foul on Theis (BOS).
Ibaka (LAC) and Brown (BOS) briefly engage and disengage as they position themselves for a potential rebound.
Williams (LAC) commits a take foul on Walker (BOS).
